Hi @prtome!

It sounds like you might be having an issue with [css specificity](https://css-tricks.com/specifics-on-css-specificity/).

If you are not using the zebra widget, this css will work on the table ([demo](http://jsfiddle.net/Mottie/856bzzeL/718/)):

```css
/* without zebra widget */
.tablesorter td.green {
    background: #006000;
    color: #fff;
}
```

If you are using the zebra widget, you'll need to increase the specificity:

```css
/* with zebra widget */
.tablesorter tbody tr td.green {
    background: #006000;
    color: #fff;
}
```

